      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "- B\xE1nh X\xE8o is a Vietnamese pancake made from rice flour, turmeric,
    and coconut milk.\n\n- The name came from the sizzling sound made while cooking
    the batter in a hot pan. It is commonly filled with shrimp, minced pork, and
    bean sprouts, then eaten with vegetables.\n\n- B\xE1nh x\xE8o is popular in Southern
    and Central Vietnam as a dish to be shared with family and friends."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f6b83f304dc3a98448bbbbe575dcc972, type: 2}
