      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "- B\xFAn Ch\u1EA3 is a Northern Vietnamese dish consisting of grilled
    pork served with rice noodles and dipping sauce.\n\n- It is especially associated
    with Hanoi and is commonly eaten for lunch.\n\n- The dish combines grilled pork
    patties, sliced pork belly, fresh herbs, and pickled vegetables.\n\n- B\xFAn
    ch\u1EA3 became internationally well known through Vietnamese street food culture."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f6b83f304dc3a98448bbbbe575dcc972, type: 2}
